            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="284c-90b2-245b-adf3">Pick a friendly **^^Cities of Sigmar Duardin^^** unit wholly within 12&quot; of this unit to be the target, then make a chanting roll of D6.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="6219-6fcc-5ae2-a6b7">If the chanting roll was 10+, you can pick another eligible unit to be a second target. Until the start of your next turn, add 1 to the Rend characteristic of each target&apos;s melee weapons.</characteristic>
