        <profile name="Steel of Helm and Heart" typeId="59b6-d47a-a68a-5dcc" typeName="Ability (Activated)" hidden="false" id="39c2-986b-b2ea-3032">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Timing" typeId="652c-3d84-4e7-14f4">Once Per Turn (Army), Any Combat Phase</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">If this unit has 5 or more models, pick an enemy unit in combat with this unit to be the target.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">If this unit is **under orders**, apply the effect below. Otherwise, roll a dice. Subtract 1 from the roll if the target is a **^^Monster^^**. On a 4+, apply the effect below.
For the rest of the turn, if this unit is in combat with the target when the target is picked to use a **^^Fight^^** ability:
• This unit must be picked to be the target of pile-in move made by the target.
• All attacks made by models in the target unit within this unit&apos;s combat range must target this unit.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="12e8-3214-7d8f-1d0f"/>
            <characteristic name="Used By" typeId="1b32-c9d6-3106-166b"/>
