            <characteristic name="Timing" typeId="652c-3d84-4e7-14f4">Once Per Turn (Army), Any Charge Phase</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">If this unit is in combat and has not charged this turn, pick an enemy unit that it is in combat with and up to 1 friendly **Freeguild Cavalier-Marshal** within this unit&apos;s combat range to be the targets.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">If this unit is **under orders**, apply the effect below. Otherwise, roll a dice. On a 3+, apply the effect below.
This unit and the friendly target can use the &apos;Charge&apos; ability even if it is not your charge phase and even if those units are in combat. Both friendly units must end that move in combat with the enemy target.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="12e8-3214-7d8f-1d0f"/>
            <characteristic name="Used By" typeId="1b32-c9d6-3106-166b"/>
