            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick this unit and up to two friendly non-**^^Monster^^** non-**^^War Machine Sigmarite^^** units if none of them have been deployed.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">Set up those units in reserve **scouting ahead**. They have now been deployed.</characteristic>
