            <characteristic name="Timing" typeId="652c-3d84-4e7-14f4">Once Per Turn (Army), Your Movement Phase</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick this unit if it is **scouting ahead**.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">Set up this unit on the battlefield wholly within 9&quot; of a battlefield edge and more than 9&quot; from all enemy units. Then, set up each other friendly unit **scouting ahead** wholly within 12&quot; of this unit and more than 9&quot; from all enemy units.</characteristic>
