            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="24f8-3803-4ab1-3b6c">Pick an objective or visible non-**^^Faction Terrain^^** terrain feature within 12&quot; of this unit to be the target. Then, make a casting roll of 2D6.</characteristic>
