            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb"/>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">If there is not a friendly **Wisper** on the battlefield, set up a friendly **Wisper** wholly within 12&quot; of this unit, visible to it and more than 9&quot; from all enemy units. This unit has summoned that **^^Manifestation^^**.</characteristic>
