                  <rules>
                    <rule name="Magisterial Platform" id="567c-2b30-d724-ceb6" hidden="true">
                      <description>Add the **Draught Horse&apos;s Iron-shod Hooves** weapons to your hero&apos;s warscroll. 
In addition, if your hero is a **Sigmarite Battlemage** or **Sigmarite Priest**, pick the &apos;Azyrite Storm&apos; or &apos;Magical Foci&apos; ability.
In addition, make the following changes to your hero&apos;s warscroll:
• Change the Move characteristic to 8&quot;.
• Change the Health characteristic to 10.
• Replace the **^^Infantry^^** keyword with the **^^War Machine^^** keyword.
If your hero is a **Sigmarite Battlemage**:
• Replace the **^^Wizard (1)^^** keyword with the **^^Wizard (2)^^** keyword.
If your hero is a **Sigmarite Battle-priest**:
• Replace the **^^Priest (1)^^** keyword with the **^^Priest (2)^^** keyword.</description>
                    </rule>
