                      <characteristics>
                        <characteristic name="Timing" typeId="652c-3d84-4e7-14f4">Deployment Phase</characteristic>
                        <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick an enemy **^^Hero^^** to be the target. You can pick a unit in reserve.</characteristic>
                        <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">Pick 1 of the following effects to apply for the rest of the battle:
***Heroic Revenge*:** If the target is slain by this unit&apos;s combat attacks, after the target is removed from play, you immediately gain 1 command point.
***Glorious Revenge**:* If the target is slain by this unit&apos;s combat attacks, you gain 30 glory points in the aftermath sequence of this  battle.
***Vendetta Fulfilled**:* If the target is slain by this unit&apos;s combat attacks, this unit gains enough renown points in the aftermath sequence of this battle to earn the next rank on its Path and it no longer has this ability</characteristic>
                        <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="12e8-3214-7d8f-1d0f"/>
                        <characteristic name="Used By" typeId="1b32-c9d6-3106-166b"/>
