                        <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick a **^^Spell^^** or **^^Prayer^^** ability that this unit can use.</characteristic>
                        <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">For the rest of the battle, this unit can use that ability in the enemy hero phase as if it were your hero phase.</characteristic>
